Subject: Windows OS upgrade
Description:
Hi Team,

We are upgrading the Windows server Operating System to Version 2022 in our system. We wanted to know does our products like Stealthaudit, Defend and SAm are compatible with the version or do we need to upgrade for 2022 OS version.

Appreciate your valuable feedback on the same.

Thanks and Regards,

Praveen V.Huilgol
What_We_Know__c: Sent customer open information about our requirements on HelpCenter
Solution_Comment__c: Yes, as per HelpCenter Article, that is fully accessible, 2022 server is supported.
